channel.title: Can't log into Hybridscape ):
channel.description:
Hello, I want to create my own private server and have some fun creating stuff but I can't seem to log into hybridscape on my Mopar client I downloaded... When I click 'Start Sever' then I log in I get a message that says... Your account is already logged in. Try again right now, or make another name.
Please, please help me ):
